      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * University of Minnesota</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:562px;\"><a href=\"/File:Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg/960px-Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg\" width=\"560\" height=\"128\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg/1280px-Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>University of Minnesota Twin Cities East Bank Campus  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>University of Minnesota Twin Cities</b>, (UM-TC, U of M, UMN)<br /> \na <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_university\">public</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Research_university\">research university</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minneapolis\">Minneapolis</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint_Paul,_Minnesota\">Saint Paul</a>, the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minneapolis%E2%80%93Saint_Paul\">Twin Cities</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minnesota\">Minnesota</a> the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\">United States</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Minnesota&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Gary_Boos\" title=\"Gary Boos\">Gary Boos</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/James_Mundstock\" title=\"James Mundstock\">James Mundstock</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/James_R._Slagle\" title=\"James R. Slagle\">James R. Slagle</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#MLStein\" title=\"Mathematician\">Marvin L. Stein</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs\">Chess Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Minnesota&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iron_Fish\" title=\"Iron Fish\">Iron Fish</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mr._Turk\" title=\"Mr. Turk\">Mr. Turk</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Minnesota&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twin-cities.umn.edu/\">University of Minnesota Twin Cities</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Minnesota\">University of Minnesota from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gopherlink.umn.edu/organization/chess\">Chess Club at the UM-TC - University of Minnesota</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chgs.elevator.umn.edu/asset/viewAsset/57f3b6787d58ae5f74bf8ba9#57f3b6d77d58ae5574bf8bcb\">Chess in the Art</a> of <a href=\"/Category:Samuel_Bak\" title=\"Category:Samuel Bak\">Samuel Bak</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chgs.elevator.umn.edu/\">Center for Holocaust &amp; Genocide Studies</a>, University of Minnesota</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://cla.umn.edu/music/ensembles-creative-work/jazz-ensembles\">U of MN Jazz Ensemble 1</a> - Thank You Very Please, Minnesota Jazz Weekend 2010, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/N8VFxtIqoOg?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Minnesota&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Panorama of mall between Northrop and Coffman Memorial Union, University of Minnesota Twin Cities <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Minnesota#East_Bank\">East Bank Campus</a>. From left: Ford Hall, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coffman_Memorial_Union\">Coffman Memorial Union</a>, Kolthoff Hall, Smith Hall (in center of image), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_Library\">Walter Library</a>, Johnston Hall, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northrop_Auditorium\">Northrop</a>, and Morrill Hall. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Northrop_Mall_panorama.jpg\">Image</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Runner1928\">Runner1928</a>,  April 25, 2014, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301052300\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.595 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 38/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 102/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:id